- system("cpu"): number of available CPUs or 1
- opposite(ring) works also for commutative global rings
  (but only, if compiled with HAVE_PLURAL)
- new library: normaliz.lib
- exotic bug in diff fixed (track 195)
- SAGE patches (4.3.1)

